### Get All Tasks
GET http://172.25.192.189:5000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json


### Update Task
PUT http://172.25.192.189:5000/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "Acheter des vivres et des boissons",
    "is_predefined": false,
    "is_done": true,
    "frequency": 7,
    "user_id": 1
}


### Delete Task
DELETE http://172.25.192.189:5000/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json


